| **Constructor Call** | Direct: `(ArmClient client, TData data)` | Indirect via reflection: `new object[] { _client, data }` |
| **Type Handling** | Strongly typed, compile-time verified | Generic `<T>`, runtime determined |
| **Flexibility** | Limited to specific resource types | Works with any resource type |
| **Use Case** | Auto-generated code for specific resources | Fallback for ad-hoc types or frameworks |

